title: Independent candidate Raza Hayat Hiraj wins NA-114 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent Candidate Raza Hayat Hiraj has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-114 Khanewal-I by securing 1,18,999 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate Syed Abid Hussain Imam, who bagged 78,296 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 58.98 percent.
